{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 30,
  "title": "第三十章（不強）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "以道佐人主。不以兵強於天下，亓事好還。"
    },
    {
      "text": "師之所居，楚棘生之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "善者果而已矣，毋以取強焉。"
    },
    {
      "text": "果而毋驕。"
    },
    {
      "text": "果而勿矜。"
    },
    {
      "text": "果而勿伐。"
    },
    {
      "text": "果而毋得已居。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂果而不強。"
    },
    {
      "text": "物壯而老，是謂之不道。"
    },
    {
      "text": "不道蚤已。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂人主能以道自輔佐也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以道自佐之主，不以兵革，順天任德，敵人自服。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其舉事好還自責，不怨於人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "農事廢，田不修。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天應之以惡氣，即害五穀，盡傷人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善用兵者，當果敢而已，不美之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不以果敢取強大之名也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "當果敢謙卑，勿自矜大也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "當果敢推讓，勿自伐取其美也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "驕，欺也。果敢勿以驕欺人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "當果敢至誠，不當逼迫不得已也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "果敢勿以為強兵、堅甲以欺凌人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "草木壯極則枯落，人壯極則衰老也。言強者不可以久。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "枯老者，坐不行道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不行道者早死。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以道佐人主，尚不可以兵强於天下，況人主躬於道者乎。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "為始者務欲立功生事，而有道者務欲還反無為，故云，其事好還也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言師凶害之物也。無有所濟，必有所傷，賊害人民，殘荒田畝，故曰荊棘生焉。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "果猶濟也。言善用師者，趣以濟難而已矣，不以兵力取强於天下也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "吾不以師道為尚，不得已而用，何矜驕之有也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言用兵雖趣功果濟難，然時故不得已，當復用者，但當以除暴亂，不遂用果以為强也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "壯，武力暴興，喻以兵强於天下者也。飄風不終朝，驟雨不終日，故暴興必不道早已也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
